           @keyframes bouncedelay {

            -webkit-transform: scale(1.0);
        }

        max-height: 100%;

    }

    .gazette-bell-launcher {
        user-select: none;
        -webkit-font-smoothing: initial;
        position: static;
        z-index: 2147483000;
        font-family: Helvetica Neue, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;
        transform: scale(1);
        transform-origin: center center;
        opacity: 1;
        height: 48px;
        width: 48px;

    .gazette-bell-launcher-button {
        width: 48px;

        border-radius: 50%;

        cursor: pointer;
        z-index: 2147483000;
        display: block;

    .gazette-bell-launcher-button svg {

           .discoverMorePrompt {
    display: block;
    background: #222222;
    color: #dddddd;
    position: fixed;
    bottom: 20px;
    right: 20px;
    border-radius: 4px;
    text-align: center;
    width: 120px;
    font-weight: 600;
    padding: 9px 5px;
    z-index: 1000;
}
.discoverMorePrompt .discoverMoreTextContainer:before {
    content: "Discover more below";
    -ms-transform: translate3D(0,0,0);
    -webkit-transform: translate3D(0,0,0);
    -moz-transform: translate3D(0,0,0);
    transform: translate3D(0,0,0);
}
.discoverMorePrompt .discoverMoreTextContainerBorderAnimation:nth-child(2) {
    -webkit-animation-delay: 5s;
    animation-delay: 5s;
}
.discoverMorePrompt .discoverMoreTextContainerBorderAnimation:nth-child(3) {
    -webkit-animation-delay: 5.1s;
    animation-delay: 5.1s;
}
    .discoverMorePrompt .discoverMoreTextContainerBorderAnimation:nth-child(4) {
    -webkit-animation-delay: 5.2s;
    animation-delay: 5.2s;
}
.discoverMorePrompt .discoverMoreTextContainerBorderAnimation {
    position: absolute;
    border: #222222 solid 4px;
    top: 0;
    right: 0;
    bottom: 0;
    left: 0;
    box-shadow: 0 0 1px transparent;
    -webkit-backface-visibility: hidden;
    backface-visibility: hidden;
    -moz-osx-font-smoothing: grayscale;
    -webkit-animation-duration: 10s;
    animation-duration: 10s;
    -webkit-animation-name: discover-more-ambient;
    animation-name: discover-more-ambient;
    -webkit-animation-iteration-count: infinite;
    animation-iteration-count: infinite;
    border-radius: 10%;
    opacity: .6;
    -ms-transform: translateZ(0);
    -webkit-transform: translateZ(0);
    -moz-transform: translateZ(0);
    transform: translateZ(0);
}
.discoverMorePrompt .tnt-svg {
    display: block;
    margin:0 auto;
    font-size: inherit;
    transform:rotate(90deg);
}
@keyframes discover-more-ambient {
    10%, 95% {top:-16px;right:-16px;bottom:-16px;left:-16px;opacity:0}
    99% {top:0px;right:0px;bottom:0px;left:0px;opacity:0}
}
